description: Open House, Sunday, May 15 from 1 to 3 pm. This well maintained home is nestled on a quiet, treed lot with a vaulted cedar ceiling, 3 season room with tile flooring near schools, parks and Hoover Reservoir! The entry is flanked by a den with built-ins and the living room which extends into the formal dining room. The open kitchen offers plenty of counter space and cabinetry, a bayed dinette open to the family room with a fireplace and built-ins. The upper level offers large main bedroom with walk-in closet, main bath with separate vanity and walk in shower. Three additional bedrooms and full bath with double vanity. The lower level recreation room adds  additional space plus an abundance of storage in the utility area and a two car garage. Enjoy the view of a beautiful fenced in back yard.

description: Great curb appeal!  This well maintained 4 bedroom home is located on cul-de-sac lot in the desirable McDot Farms subdivision.  The home features ~ 3,000 sq feet of living space!  Vaulted ceilings with beams adorn the family room. Enjoy the cold winter days staying cozy by the fireplace. Plus, there is a dedicated home office space on the 1st floor. The 2nd floor boasts a generous size owner's suite with updated bath and large walk-in closet. On this level, there are 3 add'l bedrooms and a full updated bathroom. The 4-Season room is perfect for enjoying your morning coffee, entertaining or just relaxing. 1st flr laundry. A large unfinished partial basement can be finished in the future. Great location! Selling As-Is. Showings start on Thu, 5/12.

description: Meticulously maintained 2-story home in the popular Millstone Creek subdivision. Welcoming foyer with hardwood floors, many windows to make the home bright and refreshing. 4 good sized bedrooms and a large bonus room, which makes a great TV room, play room, guest room, or second office. The Master suite has vaulted ceilings and a large master bath with soaking tub and separate shower. Make this your home.

description: Distinctively designed with nature and fun in mind.  Breathtaking views from the two story  atrium with loads of natural light.   Contemporary kitchen with new stainless appliances & slate floor.  Primary bedroom has vaulted ceiling & custom touches throughout.  Large upstairs bedrooms are joined by a catwalk that overlooks the expansive great room. Outside you will relax in the low maintenance naturalized landscaping & Wildlife Habitat.  Enjoy the outdoor kitchen including a smoker, wood fire pizza oven & grill, fully stocked and all included for you.  Its an entertainer's delight! Perfect for those who appreciate a distinctive home, far from the ordinary.  Walking distance to Elementary School, Parks & convenient to dining, entertainment, I-270 & much more.  Schedule your showing today!

description: Fantastic floor plan with first floor owner's suite, office/den and laundry with 2-story foyer and large great room - check out the new chandelier in the foyer! Gorgeous kitchen with island and new backsplash, appliances, lighting plus a custom shiplap wall between kitchen & great room! Custom cabinetry in first floor office, gas fireplace is behind wall in great room (hearth is visible), spacious bedrooms up with large loft. New roof, HVAC (3 years), appliances (2 years), garage door openers (2022), patio (2 years). attic storage, portion of basement is partially finished (ceiling). Desirable subdivision close to Alcott Elementary and Westerville Central High School.

description: Welcome home to the Madison: A 2-story floorplan, in our exclusive Smart Series, with 2-full and 1-half baths, a 3-to-4 bedrooms and a 2-car garage. This home includes a traditional front elevation with covered front porch and decorative columns. Choose from two additional architectural styles: The farmhouse elevation includes a full front porch with decorative columns, and batten board siding, or the craftsman elevation, also with a full front porch, and tapered columns, and stone and shake shingle accents. For additional space in your garage, or if you have another vehicle, select the garage extension or full 3-car garage.
